'''Adamant heraldic armour''' are pieces of the [[adamant armour]] set that have a heraldic design on them. The heraldic armour set consists of a helm, platebody and shield, which can be only obtained as a reward from [[Clue scroll (medium)|medium]] [[Treasure Trails]]. The helms, platebodies and shields are equivalent, in stats, to the [[adamant full helm]], the [[adamant platebody]] and [[adamant kiteshield]] respectively and requires a [[Defence]] level of 30 to equip.

